<Text> The US navy now says the USS Cole was being refueled when an explosion ripped through it in Yemen last week, killing 17. The revised accounting of the incident was given in a navy statement Friday raising new questions about how the small boat carrying the explosives was able to get near the ship and set off the blast.  
</Text>
